genresAdvancedInfo.name: turkish death metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Turkish death metal is a subgenre of heavy metal music that originated in Turkey. It is characterized by aggressive guitar riffs, fast-paced drumming, and growled or screamed vocals. The lyrics often deal with themes of death, darkness, and despair. Turkish death metal bands often incorporate traditional Turkish instruments and melodies into their music, creating a unique blend of Western and Eastern styles.
